we dont have very much money at all kennedy said last 
week were just squeaking 
once the hall is set up pearson believes it could draw as many 
as 90000 people annually paying a 2 entrance fee he said that 
is roughly half the number of vistors that the nearby state 
heritage center draws each year he said 
were not looking at any gigantic amount of money pearson 
said 
