the mountains of northern colorado snow also fell in western south 
dakota with 4 inches on the ground in the black hills 
eight inches of snow fell in northwestern wyoming closing 
yellowstones eastern and southern entrances sunday south of the 
park 5 inches of snow was reported in moose and jackson where 
downed power lines caused blackouts 
