could defeat him but i think it depends on the further revelations 
about what drove mr pappas to his suicide 
i would warn the republican party my own party not to make 
an issue of this bauman added 
bauman lost the seat to dyson in 1980 after bauman was charged 
with soliciting sex from a 16yearold male prostitute in 
washington the charge was later dropped although bauman 
acknowledged he was homosexual and an alcoholic 
the new york medical examiners office said an autopsy showed 
pappas death was caused by multiple internal and external 
injuries pappas fell from his 24thfloor room to an eighthfloor 
ledge 
spokeswoman ellen borakove said toxicology tests performed over 
the next week to 10 days would determine whether drugs or alcohol 
were present in his system an official classification of his 
death which police have called a suicide will await the test 
results she said 
the post article came as the federal election commission 
investigated allegations dysons campaign disclosure reports 
concealed 6650 in payments to pappas 
political consultant michael ford said he talked by phone with 
pappas about the post article for 25 minutes sunday morning pappas 
told ford he was worried that the article had irreparably damaged 
his career and had hurt dysons reelection chances the post 
reported monday 
i told him youve done nothing illegal youve done nothing 
immoral and therefore i think you can deal with this ford said 
adding he didnt think pappas was particularly depressed 
