<TEXT>
its 2 am and your baby is crying and 
wont sleep 
what to do play the beatles of course and within 15 minutes a 
hard days night becomes much easier 
awardwinning pianist floyd domino has turned the music of the 
fab four into an album of lullabies designed to send bawling 
